{"tid":950970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Whatsapp 新短訊騙案？疑似騙徒假冒中銀投資部職員【附中銀回應】","createTime":"2018-12-22T03:07:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T03:09:12.000Z","uid":51464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"54ea6b4a855e7d40e516a8b03b9cb396bd0c2a62","tid":950970,"uid":51464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T03:07:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2232272\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2232272&d=l9aZWPgK1g3ajVNLadFgEQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=942756ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2232272</a><br />\n<br />\n警方和傳媒近幾年一直呼籲提防電話騙案，相信大家對「速遞公司」和「入境處」的相關電話騙案已有所防範。不過，除了要防範電話詐騙外，《Whatsapp》等即時通訊 apps 的短訊詐騙也不容忽視。最近 Facebook Group 便流傳了一些擷圖，懷疑有騙徒偽裝成中銀證券部職員進行詐騙。<br />\n==============<br />\n騙徒：In 廢老 we trust! <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"124e2e7163527551e98ffaff613df983c836014e","tid":950970,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T03:09:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}